nodes.text: Rescue Leader was the male Naboo who led Rescue Flight during the Invasion of Naboo.

In 32 BBY, Rescue Leader led Rescue Flight in an effort to free civilians from Trade Federation prison camps. In Rescue 1, Rescue Leader freed the prisoners from Camp Three. Under cover of Bravo Flight, Rescue Leader guided Rescue Flight down the Solleu River, eventually reaching the Europa Islands. There, all people were transferred to the freighter Mercatan.
